name: Dinari HYMB
description: The Dinari HYMB dShares token (HYMB.d) represents 1:1 ownership of shares in the SPDR Nuveen Bloomberg High Yield Municipal Bond ETF (NYSE Arca: HYMB), an exchange-traded fund designed to track the performance of high-yield municipal bonds issued by U.S. states, the District of Columbia, U.S. territories, and local governments or agencies. Each HYMB.d token is fully backed by a corresponding HYMB ETF share, securely held in a transparent and auditable treasury. By leveraging blockchain technology, HYMB.d provides investors with exposure to high-yield municipal bond investments, while benefiting from 24/7 trading, fractional ownership, instant settlement, and enhanced liquidity.
